==Japanese==

===Etymology===
[[いつ]] ''[[when]]'' + the particle [[も]]

===Adverb===
'''いつも''' ([[itsumo]])
:[[何時も]] ''in kanji but usually written in hiragana.''
# [[always]], [[invariably]] 
# [[usually]]
# ''(with a negative verb)'' [[never]]

===Noun===
'''いつも''' ([[itsumo]])
:[[何時も]] ''in kanji but usually written in hiragana.''
# [[always]]
# [[usual]]

===Derived terms===
*[[いつも通り]]
*[[いつもより]]

===See also===
*[[常に]] (つねに, tsuneni)

